      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel your <strong>potatoes </strong>and chop them into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper, then peel your <strong>shallot[s] </strong>and <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
