          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2480Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, line a baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>and cut into 1 square per person</p><p>Divide the <strong>mushroom mixture</strong> evenly between the pastry squares, covering one half, then fold the pastry over the mushroom mixture to form a sealed parcel[s] (reserve the pan)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>mushroom Wellington</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2480Step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
