    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mushroom Wellington</strong> over the <strong>mash</strong> with the <strong>roasted kale</strong> to the side</p><p>Pour the <strong>onion gravy </strong>all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
